node.text:
Bacon Cheeseburger Donut anyone?👇🏼😍 You can’t go wrong a Donut to start the day. 🥓🍔🍩
Follow the recipe👇🏻
- Start with 1/4 pound patty of 80/20 ground beef
- Add it to a medium high frying pan and season heavily with salt
- Cook to your liking, add a slice of cheddar cheese, and remove from heat
- Place another slice of cheddar cheese on top of a soft hamburger bun and place the burger on top
- Add a few slices of bacon making sure to keep the middle open
- Add some ketchup and mustard to the top bun and press it into the burger to flatten it out
- Using a small cookie cutter, cut out the middle
- Submerge the burger in a bowl of beaten eggs and then cover it in panko breadcrumbs
- Fry the burger in a shallow pan of cooking oil at 375 for 3 minutes a side, or in an air fryer at 370 for 5 minutes each side
👉🏼 Follow @tradefoods for more, & TAG YOUR FRIENDS👇🏼awesome creations by my buddy @thejoshelkin 🍳🥪
